{"word":"G4357 - προσμένω - prosménō - pros-men'-o - Abide still","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">προσμένω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">prosménō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pros-men'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Abide still</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - தங்கியிரு, தரித்திரு, நிலைத்திரு"},{"paragraph":"to remain still"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4314 - πρός - prós - pros/4314\">G4314</a> and <a href=\"#/G3306 - μένω - ménō - men'-o/3306\">G3306</a>; to <i>stay further</i>, that is, <i>remain</i> in a place, with a person; figuratively to <i>adhere</i> to, <i>persevere</i> in: - abide still, be with, cleave unto, continue in (with).</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}